com.saxonica.xsltextn.pedigree

Class PedigreeMapItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saxonica.xsltextn.pedigree.DelegatingMapItem
      • com.saxonica.xsltextn.pedigree.PedigreeMapItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PedigreeValue, Callable, MapItem, Function, GroundedValue, Item, Sequence

    public class PedigreeMapItem
extends DelegatingMapItem
implements MapItem, PedigreeValue
    A PedigreeMapItem represents an XDM map together with a Pedigree: that is, retained information about how the map was selected within a JSON-like tree.
